      • execute

        int execute​(int timeUnits)
        Simulate execution of cpu burst for timeUnits time. If this cpu burst can complete in the given time, the method returns the quantity of unused time units. If this burst cannot complete in the given time then the method returns a -ve value, n, where -n represents the amount of burst time remaining.
        Returns:
        timeUnits-this.getBurstRemaining().
